    • Field Detail

      • PREDICATE_ID

        static final String PREDICATE_ID
        Annotation is used to tag the StatementPatternNodes in a JoinGroupNode with the identified assigned to the corresponding IPredicate. This makes it possible to lookup the SPO from the IPredicate when the RTO hands us back an ordered join path.
